{"tid":403163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登 充斥住一大堆 「道德低地撚」, 凡事都訴諸於道德撚","createTime":"2017-09-17T03:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T09:22:26.000Z","uid":62935,"like":22,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55e4ed6def8721cc1014afe6fc8562f4a9b8efac","tid":403163,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"連登開始充斥住一堆 「道德低地撚」<br />\n<br />\n佢地的特徵係 事無大小 都搵個位入講d on9野，<br />\n正常人見到都會回應屌鳩佢地，<br />\n呢個時候「道德低地撚」就會反駁你係道德撚：因為你懶有道德先唔認同佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<br />\n城巴兇案 男疑兇父親：對唔住，唔好意思，我個仔都冇晒前途喇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/403081?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/403081?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n正常人見到都會知道件老野咁講係無腦兼白痴<br />\n但「道德低地撚」會點都搵位入 屌你道德撚<br />\n縱然件事同 道德 不 道德 根本毫無關係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實總結一句<br />\n呢班只係心智未成熟的中二病撚為左嘩眾取寵講d on9野引人注意搏屌的一班人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2c1bac882017b5118007b27fba748d55f101e5","tid":403163,"uid":8253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:44:56.000Z","msg":"縱然件事同 道德 不 道德 根本毫無關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87b6eb3b7e22183b9fea52dce36a9d4e912c74b","tid":403163,"uid":62935,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>縱然件事同 道德 不 道德 根本毫無關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重點係佢地以自己 無道德 自詡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\